          <p class="investment"><strong>Investment:</strong> $59K | <strong>Outcomes:</strong> 3-4 AI models operational, 75% staff using dashboards</p>
        </div>

        <div class="phase">
          <h3>Phase 3: Optimization & Sustainability (Year 3)</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Advanced analytics (resource allocation, curriculum effectiveness)</li>
            <li>AI tutoring assistant launch</li>
